Detailed Description

ReplyPacket for the IDTranslationRequestPacket.

The nodes in the packet are identified by their positions in the vectors.
PosSizeComment
X 4 bytes Map id @ endrow
X + 4 4 bytes User defined data. Should be copied to the reply
X + 8 1 byte Flags. Bit zero is translateToLower.
X + 9 3 bytes Unused.
X + 12 4 bytes Unused.
X + 16 4 bytes Nbr of nodevectors.
X + 20 4 bytes*nbr of nodevectors Sizes of nodevectors start here
Each nodevector consists of:
PosSizeComment
Y 8 bytes*nbrNodes mapid, nodeid
